  <source>Cliniques universitaires Saint-Luc- Université Catholique de Louvain</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of these studies is to determine whether vestibular disorders could affect
      visuo-spatial cognition. Visuo-spatial cognition will be evaluated using a new questionnaire
      and a new computerized test using a digital tablet in different studies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
